  cask "obsidian"
  #  4. https://culturedcode.com/things/ ; "award-winning personal task manager that helps you achieve your goals. "
  mas "Things", id: 904280696
  #  5. https://www.mozilla.org/firefox/developer/; Open Source web browser w/ CSS Grid utils & other fancy stuff. Also BLUE
  cask "firefox-developer-edition"
  #  6. It's Tweetbot - remember from the menu bar? (L:11.)  https://tapbots.com/tweetbot/mac/
  #  7. Adobe Photoshop; Its here and I'm trying to get better acquainted with it, but secretly I still go to
  mas "com.pixelmatorteam.pixelmator.x", id: 1289583905 # a lot of the time if I need to do a quick thing.
